{
  "stem": "21319.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They went to gymnasium before the First World War.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they, at that time, they could learn-- it was-- Russia was, I think, influenced or was occupied.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Russia occupied.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think, Vilna was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They kept the city of Lithuania.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Russia was-- was-- was under occupation of Russia, until the Second World War.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So that's why-- no, I'm thinking the First World War.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But that time, when Poland got Vilna, Russian, if you learned Russian, if they find that someone-- if-- it was like a death sentence.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You went to prison, and that was it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So German, Polish, speak Russian, Yiddish, Hebrew, and this is the languages.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But my sister, the one who is senile, suffers from Alzheimer, the one from Cuba, who lives in Florida.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember about five, six, years ago when I visited, you know, still-- she still recognize me then.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then I ask her about-- if, you know, talking about languages, she spoke French.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She still remembers in Russian and German, and natural, Spanish and Italian.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She speaks about 10 languages.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But despite the fact that her head is not-- she started to speak to me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I couldn't believe it, you know, honestly.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was beautiful.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was great.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a lot of poor-- a lot of poor Jewish people, and a lot of poor people in Vilna.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I remember we-- we used to help them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My mother used to you know, elicit strangers eating at her table.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And many times I used to get hungry.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was, I don't know, about 10, 12 years.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I used to say to her, you know, over the weekends and holidays, I said, ma, why can't we have just our family?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I had my grandfather and mine uncles.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my cousins used to come.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
